      interface  ISourceProcessorUpdateVulnsOnTarget
      This marker interface is to be implemented by the main processor implementation that updates the target with updated vulnerability data for vulnerabilities previously submitted by a corresponding ISourceProcessorSubmitVulnsToTarget.

    • Uses of IProcessor in com.fortify.processrunner.processor

      Classes in com.fortify.processrunner.processor that implement IProcessor 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractCompositeProcessor
      This abstract IProcessor implementation provides support for invoking a list of individual IProcessor instances.
      class  AbstractProcessor
      This abstract IProcessor implementation allows subclasses to implement only specific processing phases by overriding the AbstractProcessor.preProcess(Context), AbstractProcessor.process(Context) and/or AbstractProcessor.postProcess(Context) methods respectively.
      class  AbstractProcessorBuildObjectMapFromGroupedObjects
      This abstract class allows for building an object map from grouped objects.
      class  AbstractProcessorBuildObjectMapsFromGroupedObjects
      This abstract class allows for building a object maps from grouped objects.
      class  AbstractProcessorGroupByExpressions
      This IProcessor implementation allows for collecting and grouping data stored in the Context during the Phase#PROCESS phase.
      class  CompositeOrderedProcessor
      This CompositeProcessor implementation will dynamically re-order the list of IProcessor instances based on the current value of the Ordered.getOrder() method for each IProcessor, whenever the CompositeOrderedProcessor.getProcessors() method is called.
      class  CompositeProcessor
      This IProcessor implementation allows a list of individual IProcessor instances to be configured using the constructor or CompositeProcessor.addProcessors(IProcessor...) method.
      Methods in com.fortify.processrunner.processor that return types with arguments of type IProcessor 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      protected List<IProcessor> CompositeProcessor.getProcessors()
      Get the list of configured IProcessor instances that make up this composite processor.
      protected List<IProcessor> CompositeOrderedProcessor.getProcessors()
      This method retrieves the currently configured IProcessor instances from our superclass, and returns them in a sorted order.
      protected abstract List<IProcessor> AbstractCompositeProcessor.getProcessors()
      Concrete subclasses must implement this method to return the list of individual IProcessor implementations that make up this composite processor.
      Methods in com.fortify.processrunner.processor with parameters of type IProcessor 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void CompositeProcessor.addProcessors(IProcessor... processors)
      Configure the list of IProcessor instances that make up this composite processor.
